# GoMine Proxy List — 1 proxy per line (1 per account)
# Format: socks5://host:port or http://host:port
# If proxy.txt is missing or not enough lines, falls back to socks5://127.0.0.1:1080
#
# Example:
socks5://127.0.0.1:1080
# socks5://proxy2.example.com:1080
# http://user:pass@proxy3.example.com:8080
